but if you break the agreement,

246
00:21:29,400 --> 00:21:30,440
you'll be punished.

247
00:21:33,160 --> 00:21:34,080
What a load of..

248
00:21:37,760 --> 00:21:39,240
The truth is, he never graduated in Law.

249
00:21:40,600 --> 00:21:42,080
He got expelled from Harvard first.

250
00:21:43,120 --> 00:21:44,680
P'Jane got expelled?

251
00:21:58,480 --> 00:22:00,760
Harvard student expelled

252
00:22:01,280 --> 00:22:03,440
