I've been looking for a way to take him down.

291
00:24:38,920 --> 00:24:40,280
But I don't get it.

292
00:24:42,480 --> 00:24:43,880
What does this have to do with me?

293
00:24:46,000 --> 00:24:47,840
I don't have any power.

294
00:24:50,880 --> 00:24:53,080
He likes luring people into his trap.

295
00:24:53,960 --> 00:24:54,960
Making them indebted to him.

296
00:24:55,960 --> 00:24:58,280
Or telling them that they're special.

297
00:24:59,680 --> 00:25:01,080
That he can make their dreams

298
00:25:01,080 --> 00:25:02,480
really come true.

299
00:25:04,360 --> 00:25:06,560
Has he ever said anything like that to you?

300
00:25:08,840 --> 00:25:10,680
Jane, you're far more special than I realized.

301
00:25:11,360 --> 00:25:13,040
More special than anyone I've ever met.

302
00:25:49,680 --> 00:25:50,680
(Congratulations to the new Student President)

303
00:25:50,680 --> 00:25:51,840
(Toy Rattawit Meechai)

304
00:25:55,960 --> 00:25:57,360
I also have no clue

305
00:25:58,360 --> 00:26:00,040
why he's taken such an interest in you.

306
00:26:01,080 --> 00:26:03,360
But I think he's been manipulating you.

307
00:26:03,680 --> 00:26:04,880
Just like he does with everyone else.

308
00:26:11,280 --> 00:26:12,760
Stay away from him.

309
00:26:13,800 --> 00:26:15,080
I don't want to see you

310
00:26:15,640 --> 00:26:17,240
get hurt later.

311
00:26:22,680 --> 00:26:23,920
But if you still don't believe me,

312
00:26:25,680 --> 00:26:26,760
next time he does something

313
00:26:26,760 --> 00:26:28,040
and doesn't tell you about it,

314
00:26:29,480 --> 00:26:31,680
try following him and see for yourself.

315
00:26:33,320 --> 00:26:34,880
He might be carrying out a favor.

316
00:26:42,920 --> 00:26:45,040
(Big Jane: See you tomorrow.)

317
00:26:45,040 --> 00:26:49,360
(Big Jane: What are you doing, Jane?)

318
00:27:54,360 --> 00:27:55,960
We've only been apart for one night.

319
00:27:57,280 --> 00:27:59,280
I miss you already.

320
00:28:04,600 --> 00:28:05,560
What are you doing, P'Jane?

321
00:28:07,760 --> 00:28:08,360
P'Jane.

322
00:28:30,680 --> 00:28:31,440
P'Jane.

323
00:29:17,480 --> 00:29:18,280
P'Jane!

324
00:29:23,360 --> 00:29:24,240
I'm not in the mood.

325
00:29:27,960 --> 00:29:28,760
Why?

326
00:29:31,360 --> 00:29:33,200
What are you still suspicious of?

327
00:29:37,360 --> 00:29:38,760
I've answered all your questions.

328
00:29:44,760 --> 00:29:46,560
Why don't you trust me?

329
00:29:54,560 --> 00:29:56,080
Why did you approach me in the first place?

330
00:29:59,240 --> 00:30:00,120
I already told you.

331
00:30:01,080 --> 00:30:02,240
Because you're special.

332
00:30:03,040 --> 00:30:05,120
He likes luring people into his trap.

333
00:30:05,280 --> 00:30:07,480
Or telling them that they're special.

334
00:30:12,720 --> 00:30:13,720
You say that to everyone

335
00:30:13,720 --> 00:30:15,280
who makes a contract with you, don't you?

336
00:30:21,960 --> 00:30:22,640
Do you know something?

337
00:30:24,680 --> 00:30:26,640
I hate being manipulated more than anything.

338
00:30:49,280 --> 00:30:50,560
I've never manipulated you.

339
00:31:06,440 --> 00:31:07,240
You should answer that call.

340
00:31:08,760 --> 00:31:09,880
I'll come back later.

341
00:31:27,560 --> 00:31:28,360
Hello?

342
00:32:29,360 --> 00:32:31,160
I told you not to call me.

343
00:32:32,720 --> 00:32:33,880
I forgot.

344
00:32:36,920 --> 00:32:38,720
I'm really grateful.

345
00:32:38,720 --> 00:32:40,200
Thank you so much.

346
00:32:41,080 --> 00:32:43,240
If there's ever anything you want me to do,

347
00:32:43,640 --> 00:32:45,760
just let me know.

348
00:32:46,840 --> 00:32:48,160
What do you want me to do?

349
00:32:49,720 --> 00:32:50,840
Whatever you want me to do,

350
00:32:50,840 --> 00:32:51,960
just tell me.

351
00:33:08,360 --> 00:33:09,560
Come here, Jane.

352
00:33:18,080 --> 00:33:19,160
Why don't you tell him

353
00:33:20,720 --> 00:33:22,480
what I did for you?

354
00:33:24,160 --> 00:33:24,960
Well...

355
00:33:25,760 --> 00:33:27,160
my house burned down.

356
00:33:27,840 --> 00:33:28,520
And...

357
00:33:29,200 --> 00:33:30,480
I practically lost everything.

358
00:33:31,280 --> 00:33:32,800
So I came to ask P'Jane

359
00:33:33,160 --> 00:33:33,960
for help.

360
00:33:34,760 --> 00:33:35,560
Then P'Jane...

361
00:33:36,000 --> 00:33:37,080
P'Jane raised money

362
00:33:37,640 --> 00:33:38,800
from the Student Council.

363
00:33:39,320 --> 00:33:40,480
So I could continue my studies.

364
00:33:42,120 --> 00:33:43,240
Tomorrow this story will be published

365
00:33:43,240 --> 00:33:44,840
on our university's news website.

366
00:33:47,160 --> 00:33:48,880
They just won't mention that P'Jane helped me.

367
00:33:54,360 --> 00:33:55,080
You can go now.

368
00:33:55,960 --> 00:33:58,440
Next time, just send me a message to thank me.

369
00:34:00,200 --> 00:34:02,120
No need to arrange a meeting like this.

370
00:34:02,360 --> 00:34:03,160
Of course.

371
00:34:03,480 --> 00:34:04,280
Thank you.

372
00:34:15,880 --> 00:34:17,280
I really don't get it.

373
00:34:19,320 --> 00:34:21,560
If you're using your network to do good things like this,

374
00:34:23,480 --> 00:34:24,800
then why does everyone keep saying

375
00:34:25,080 --> 00:34:26,480
that you're a terrible person?

376
00:34:28,679 --> 00:34:29,679
Because of prejudice.

377
00:34:32,679 --> 00:34:34,360
I think the person who is manipulating you

378
00:34:36,639 --> 00:34:37,639
isn't me

379
00:34:41,360 --> 00:34:43,639
but I think it's someone who hates me.

380
00:35:01,280 --> 00:35:02,480
This key.

381
00:35:04,320 --> 00:35:05,800
I've never given it to anyone before.

382
00:35:08,800 --> 00:35:11,120
It's a symbol of my trust.

383
00:35:14,200 --> 00:35:15,520
And a promise.

384
00:35:17,160 --> 00:35:19,280
That you can ask me anything.

385
00:35:23,040 --> 00:35:25,000
And I'll answer everything

386
00:35:29,280 --> 00:35:30,240
you want to know.

387
00:35:41,920 --> 00:35:43,560
Is there still anything you're suspicious about?

388
00:36:03,800 --> 00:36:04,280
Do you..

389
00:36:05,280 --> 00:36:06,800
really love me?

390
00:36:12,520 --> 00:36:13,280
Of course I do.

391
00:37:12,160 --> 00:37:13,440
The Sakwarakul family,

392
00:37:13,440 --> 00:37:15,160
owners of Trust Communication

393
00:37:15,160 --> 00:37:16,680
and ShopChill E-Commerce,

394
00:37:16,680 --> 00:37:19,720
have denied reports of a management reshuffle.

395
00:37:19,720 --> 00:37:21,560
Mr. Chalerm Sakwarakul,

396
00:37:21,560 --> 00:37:24,800
the current CEO, will remain in his position.

397
00:37:24,800 --> 00:37:28,000
And his business empire continues to stand strong.

398
00:37:31,560 --> 00:37:32,800
How's it going?

399
00:37:33,120 --> 00:37:34,160
A lot of customers lately?

400
00:37:34,880 --> 00:37:35,600
Argh.

401
00:37:36,120 --> 00:37:37,160
Not really.

402
00:37:37,680 --> 00:37:39,520
Only you and Put show up.

403
00:37:40,320 --> 00:37:42,040
When is your bike gonna break down?

404
00:37:42,040 --> 00:37:42,560
Oh!

405
00:37:42,560 --> 00:37:43,880
So you can finally buy a new one from me.

406
00:37:44,280 --> 00:37:45,280
It's gonna be hard. There's someone waiting for you.

407
00:37:46,480 --> 00:37:48,600
There, someone's waiting.

408
00:37:55,560 --> 00:37:56,360
Jane.

409
00:37:57,720 --> 00:37:59,160
How'd you come here?

410
00:38:00,040 --> 00:38:01,080
I asked Put.

411
00:38:03,360 --> 00:38:05,080
Do you need something from me?

412
00:38:11,400 --> 00:38:12,760
I want to know about Tee.

413
00:38:15,960 --> 00:38:17,040
You know what

414
00:38:17,400 --> 00:38:18,560
happened to him, right?

415
00:38:21,160 --> 00:38:22,560
Then why don't we go ask him ourselves?

416
00:38:31,280 --> 00:38:54,800
(Restricted Area: No Entry)

417
00:39:09,000 --> 00:39:09,920
I'll wait outside.

418
00:39:10,880 --> 00:39:11,960
You go in alone.

419
00:39:18,960 --> 00:39:29,040
(Restricted Area: No Entry)

420
00:39:45,480 --> 00:39:46,520
What's up?

421
00:39:47,120 --> 00:39:48,240
Haven't seen you in ages.

422
00:39:51,080 --> 00:39:51,680
Hey.

423
00:39:53,320 --> 00:39:54,880
What happened to you?

424
00:39:57,560 --> 00:39:58,880
Was it P'Jane?

425
00:39:59,280 --> 00:40:00,080
Why?

426
00:40:00,560 --> 00:40:01,520
Did he send you here?

427
00:40:01,920 --> 00:40:02,960
He already got me thrown in prison.

428
00:40:03,240 --> 00:40:04,320
What else does he want from me?

429
00:40:04,320 --> 00:40:04,960
Tee.

430
00:40:06,000 --> 00:40:06,880
Calm down first.

431
00:40:13,720 --> 00:40:15,160
I just want to ask you something.

432
00:40:17,720 --> 00:40:18,760
You really asked P'Jane

433
00:40:19,720 --> 00:40:21,960
to make you Student Council President, right?

434
00:40:33,080 --> 00:40:34,960
But if you had a contract with him,

435
00:40:37,320 --> 00:40:39,560
why did he suddenly have you sent to prison?

436
00:40:42,160 --> 00:40:43,760
Because one of God Jane's people

437
00:40:43,760 --> 00:40:46,280
wanted my position.

438
00:40:52,440 --> 00:40:53,560
The guy named Toy?

439
00:40:54,680 --> 00:40:55,360
Yeah.

440
00:40:57,440 --> 00:40:58,760
Another one of his lackeys.

441
00:41:00,120 --> 00:41:01,400
I refused to give up my position.

442
00:41:01,880 --> 00:41:03,080
So he kicked me out.

443
00:41:03,600 --> 00:41:04,920
By having me thrown in here.

444
00:41:06,600 --> 00:41:08,080
Do you know someone named Jui?

445
00:41:10,840 --> 00:41:12,640
Her ex came looking for her.

446
00:41:14,360 --> 00:41:15,960
But Jui said it was P'Jane's doing.

447
00:41:17,480 --> 00:41:18,240
What did you just say?

448
00:41:19,840 --> 00:41:21,400
Champ dragged her back?

449
00:41:23,880 --> 00:41:25,920
No wonder she never came to bail me out.

450
00:41:29,600 --> 00:41:31,360
So you're the guy Jui was cheating with?

451
00:41:32,520 --> 00:41:34,280
She told me she'd already broken up with Champ.

452
00:41:36,720 --> 00:41:38,560
How much does that bastard God Jane hate me?

453
00:41:40,200 --> 00:41:42,240
He's definitely trying to stop me from getting bail.

454
00:41:55,520 --> 00:41:56,440
What's up, Put?

455
00:41:59,200 --> 00:42:00,840
I brought Jane to see Tee.

456
00:42:12,920 --> 00:42:13,560
So did you really embezzle money

457
00:42:13,560 --> 00:42:15,040
from the Student Council?

458
00:42:19,600 --> 00:42:20,680
I did so much for the university.

459
00:42:21,080 --> 00:42:22,600
I deserved some compensation.

460
00:42:26,120 --> 00:42:27,760
But if you hadn't stolen money from the university

461
00:42:28,880 --> 00:42:30,360
or from the volunteer camp funds,

462
00:42:32,160 --> 00:42:33,600
you wouldn't be in here.

463
00:42:35,920 --> 00:42:37,120
What the hell is your problem?

464
00:42:37,520 --> 00:42:38,920
Why are you defending him?

465
00:42:40,760 --> 00:42:42,160
P'Jane is my boyfriend.

466
00:42:44,960 --> 00:42:46,160
Have you lost your mind?

467
00:42:47,680 --> 00:42:48,760
But I'm not defending him

468
00:42:48,760 --> 00:42:49,840
because he's my boyfriend.

469
00:42:51,960 --> 00:42:52,880
From what I've heard,

470
00:42:53,920 --> 00:42:55,520
both you and Jui were in the wrong.

471
00:42:56,400 --> 00:42:57,640
Yet you're blaming someone else.

472
00:42:58,040 --> 00:42:59,200
And your P'Jane??

473
00:42:59,200 --> 00:43:00,240
Is he really that great?

474
00:43:00,440 --> 00:43:00,920
Huh?

475
00:43:09,400 --> 00:43:11,400
You know the Sakwarakul family, right?

476
00:43:18,680 --> 00:43:19,880
The ones who own the mobile network company.

477
00:43:20,960 --> 00:43:21,760
Yeah.

478
00:43:23,040 --> 00:43:24,560
P'Jane belongs to that family.

479
00:43:32,960 --> 00:43:34,600
His surname is Plakorn.

480
00:43:36,440 --> 00:43:37,720
That's someone else's surname.

481
00:43:39,920 --> 00:43:40,760
But in reality,

482
00:43:41,320 --> 00:43:43,720
P'Jane is the eldest son of that family.

483
00:43:45,760 --> 00:43:46,440
Do you understand now

484
00:43:46,960 --> 00:43:48,560
why God Jane has been pulling the strings

485
00:43:48,560 --> 00:43:49,960
behind the university network?

486
00:43:51,280 --> 00:43:52,400
Because he doesn't want anything

487
00:43:52,400 --> 00:43:53,600
to damage that family's reputation.

488
00:43:55,200 --> 00:43:55,960
Listen to me.

489
00:43:57,160 --> 00:43:58,080
That bastard God Jane

490
00:43:58,480 --> 00:44:00,360
is no different from a mafia boss.

491
00:44:00,920 --> 00:44:01,880
Stay away from him.

492
00:44:03,160 --> 00:44:05,400
He'll use you until you're no longer useful.

493
00:44:05,400 --> 00:44:06,560
Then he'll throw you away.

494
00:44:06,560 --> 00:44:07,880
Just like he threw me away!!

495
00:44:18,280 --> 00:44:21,280
(Restricted Area: No Entry)

496
00:44:23,120 --> 00:44:23,960
Jane.

497
00:44:32,320 --> 00:44:33,080
Are you okay?

498
00:44:38,120 --> 00:44:39,280
Put called me.

499
00:44:40,360 --> 00:44:41,480
He said P'Jane asked to clear things up.

500
00:44:42,600 --> 00:44:43,440
Why does P'Jane want to clear things up with him?

501
00:44:44,480 --> 00:44:45,360
He already knows

502
00:44:46,440 --> 00:44:47,880
that Put brought you to see me.

503
00:44:48,440 --> 00:44:49,640
So now he's suspicious of him.

504
00:44:51,280 --> 00:44:52,280
I was careless.

505
00:44:53,280 --> 00:44:55,040
I didn't think he'd catch on so quickly.

506
00:44:59,320 --> 00:45:00,640
Where did P'Jane ask him to meet?

507
00:45:01,480 --> 00:45:02,520
Take me there.

508
00:45:10,480 --> 00:45:11,080
Excuse me.

509
00:45:13,560 --> 00:45:14,680
Are you a member here?

510
00:45:15,160 --> 00:45:16,840
Only members are allowed inside.

511
00:45:31,320 --> 00:45:32,360
Put isn't answering.

512
00:45:33,560 --> 00:45:35,080
I guess they're still talking.

513
00:45:59,880 --> 00:46:01,520
I already have an appointment with P'Jane.

514
00:46:12,360 --> 00:46:13,160
All set, sir.

515
00:46:17,760 --> 00:46:18,560
Wait.

516
00:46:19,760 --> 00:46:21,360
Only people with a card may enter.

517
00:46:21,360 --> 00:46:22,320
Follow me inside.

518
00:46:27,960 --> 00:46:28,880
I'll go by myself.

519
00:46:32,880 --> 00:46:33,680
Be careful.

520
00:46:59,200 --> 00:46:59,720
Alright.

521
00:47:00,480 --> 00:47:01,240
Wait here.

522
00:47:02,320 --> 00:47:03,320
If someone comes out,

523
00:47:03,640 --> 00:47:04,600
then you can go in.

524
00:48:17,680 --> 00:48:19,480
Why are you interfering between me and Jane?

525
00:48:31,880 --> 00:48:32,760
Jane asked me to.

526
00:48:34,040 --> 00:48:35,680
He wanted to know about you.

527
00:48:39,640 --> 00:48:41,080
And why was it your business

528
00:48:42,080 --> 00:48:43,840
to take Jane to see Dan?

529
00:48:57,960 --> 00:48:59,480
Stop staying silent and say something.

530
00:49:03,280 --> 00:49:04,080
I...

531
00:49:08,640 --> 00:49:09,840
I...

532
00:49:10,480 --> 00:49:12,640
I want to make a blood pact with you.

533
00:49:15,360 --> 00:49:16,440
I want to ask

534
00:49:17,880 --> 00:49:19,480
that you leave Jane alone.

535
00:49:25,200 --> 00:49:27,240
And what are you offering in exchange?

536
00:49:37,360 --> 00:49:39,080
You can ask anything of me.

537
00:49:41,560 --> 00:49:43,200
I'd even trade my life.

538
00:49:52,760 --> 00:49:55,160
Your life isn't worth that much, Put.

539
00:50:04,680 --> 00:50:05,480
Why?

540
00:50:07,680 --> 00:50:09,080
Do you like Jane?

541
00:50:20,960 --> 00:50:21,800
And what about you?

542
00:50:23,800 --> 00:50:25,240
Do you like him or are you just using him?

543
00:50:30,360 --> 00:50:31,200
If you're getting involved with him

544
00:50:31,200 --> 00:50:32,360
without really caring about him,

545
00:50:33,880 --> 00:50:34,560
then I'll be the one

546
00:50:35,520 --> 00:50:37,840
to take Jane out of your life myself.

547
00:50:46,920 --> 00:50:48,360
Who do you think you are

548
00:50:49,840 --> 00:50:51,440
to order me around?

549
00:50:53,440 --> 00:50:54,360
You do know,

550
00:50:55,360 --> 00:50:56,360
what someone like me

551
00:50:57,840 --> 00:50:58,960
is capable of doing to you, right?

552
00:51:08,720 --> 00:51:09,520
Stop!

553
00:51:12,360 --> 00:51:13,160
Jane.

554
00:51:14,560 --> 00:51:16,160
Don't do anything to Put.

555
00:51:25,240 --> 00:51:26,040
Stay back.

556
00:51:33,080 --> 00:51:34,440
I can't believe this.

557
00:51:41,920 --> 00:51:43,280
Jane, listen to me first.

558
00:51:48,000 --> 00:51:49,640
Didn't you say you had nothing to hide?

559
00:51:54,160 --> 00:51:56,080
I know everything about Jui and Tee now.

560
00:51:57,640 --> 00:51:58,760
Who do you think you are

561
00:52:00,160 --> 00:52:02,760
to control other people's lives however you want?

562
00:52:05,440 --> 00:52:06,840
Including mine.

563
00:52:16,840 --> 00:52:17,560
Listen.

564
00:52:19,320 --> 00:52:21,000
I've never controlled your life.

565
00:52:25,720 --> 00:52:26,840
That's enough.

566
00:52:29,040 --> 00:52:31,160
I've been trying to protect you.

567
00:52:32,160 --> 00:52:33,880
I've been trying to trust you all this time.

568
00:52:36,400 --> 00:52:38,920
But all you've done is keep hiding things from me.

569
00:52:42,080 --> 00:52:43,480
Do you think I'm stupid?

570
00:52:45,480 --> 00:52:47,960
I hate myself whenever I'm around you.

571
00:52:53,080 --> 00:52:54,680
Let's stop seeing each other, P'Jane.

572
00:52:58,760 --> 00:53:00,440
I don't want to see your face anymore.

573
00:53:18,880 --> 00:53:20,480
You're such a liar.

574
00:53:24,080 --> 00:53:25,400
Wasn't this necklace supposed to be a promise

575
00:53:25,400 --> 00:53:26,840
that you'd always tell me the truth?

576
